assets.description: frame of my custom built single wheel motorcycle trailer featured @vertigoprops . not to scale. for reference, use mountain bike shock and wheelbarrow wheel with frame mterial of 1 in square tubing. the real life trailer can support more load than the motorcycle should tow. the flexible design of the wheel assembly reduces unsprung weight by 50%, this means an increase in tire traction and less spring hop, at the cost of higher shift in center of gravity during turns. the solution is, dont speed through corners, the bike is very stable.

assets.description:
Microcosm and macrocosm, worlds within worlds, fractals, every molecule holds the universe.
From a crystal forest, the roots run deep, just below the surface another world exists, and often there is more hidden beneath the earth, than we can imagine. These roots anchor us, and keep our higher selves grounded and real in the 3d world, while our souls are mirrored into infinity. We are part angel and part animal, a channel between the heavens and the earth, and are reflected in the stars.
